Process called "compute_weierstrass_zeta" that takes z as Float, invariants as WeierstrassInvariants, config as EllipticConfig returns Float:
    Note: Compute Weierstrass zeta function ζ(z) - logarithmic derivative of sigma
    Note: TODO: Implement ζ(z) with quasi-periodicity and relation to ℘(z)
